cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper deals with unsupervised training of deep neural networks for computer vision tasks such as segmentation, image matting, and dehazing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new approach for training deep neural networks using task-specific energy functions, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper includes experiments and results, which could also place it under the category of graphics (cs.GR).
